text: Jiantang or Gyaitang is a town in northern Yunnan, seat of Shangri-La County and Dêqên Tibetan Autonomous Prefecture. ==Climate== Jiantang has a subtropical highland climate (Cwb) with little to no rainfall from November to April and moderate to heavy rainfall from May to October. ==References== Category:Township-level divisions of Diqing Tibetan Autonomous Prefecture
title: Jiantang
